code: export const decodeToken=token=>{if(!token){return null;}const base64Url=token.split('.')[1];const base64=base64Url.replace(/-/g,'+').replace(/_/g,'/');const jsonPayload=decodeURIComponent(atob(base64).split('').map(function(c){return'%'+('00'+c.charCodeAt(0).toString(16)).slice(-2);}).join(''));return JSON.parse(jsonPayload);};
